rows.label: qst650106_msg0001
rows.name:
It's just as the information T-elos
Re: got out of them said...

rows.label: qst650106_msg0002
rows.name: What's the plan?

rows.label: qst650106_msg0003
rows.name:
Now that we know we're being targeted,
we have to deal with it, but...

rows.label: qst650106_msg0004
rows.name: But fighting blindly is...

rows.label: qst650106_msg0005
rows.name:
They are an irreconcilable
enemy. We must destroy them...

rows.label: qst650106_msg0006
rows.name: T-elos Re:...?

rows.label: qst650106_msg0007
rows.name: Hey!

rows.label: qst650106_msg0008
rows.name:
It seems your preparations
aren't finished...

rows.label: qst650106_msg0009
rows.name:
With just one slow-looking
thing, you have no hope of
defeating the Aegis's party.

rows.label: qst650106_msg0010
rows.name: You're...!?

rows.label: qst650106_msg0011
rows.name: Have they made the first move!?

rows.label: qst650106_msg0012
rows.name:
No, this is convenient.
It saves us the trouble
of finding the Aegis...

rows.label: qst650106_msg0013
rows.name: Like a moth to a flame.

rows.label: qst650106_msg0014
rows.name:
The survivors of Acedia will
be gathering here soon.

rows.label: qst650106_msg0015
rows.name:
If we can hold out until then,
we can have our revenge!

rows.label: qst650106_msg0016
rows.name: Hmph... Interesting.

rows.label: qst650106_msg0017
rows.name: It seems you all think the same way.

rows.label: qst650106_msg0018
rows.name:
Not knowing you'll all be
tortured in the same way...

rows.label: qst650106_msg0019
rows.name:
A mere Blade! Do not
underestimate our power!

rows.label: qst650106_msg0020
rows.name: Let's go!

rows.label: qst650106_msg0021
rows.name: Hmph... Entertain me.
